sentences: Since 1999 he released five albums, several 12-inch singles and MP3s / WAVs starting out on Düsseldorf's Label Unique Records.
Since 2004 he releases on Hamburg based Moonbootique, on Norman Cook's Southern Fried Records, on A-Trak's Fool's Gold, on Steve Aoki's Dim Mak Records and Malente's own Label No Brainer Records.
In 2007 as well as in 2009 he has been voted Top National Act of the German Club Charts (DCC).
